!========================== LoKiHlt v2r8 2010-03-17 ===========================
! 2010-03-12 - Vanya Belyaev

 - major change in L0_(SUM)DECISION, dollowing the changes 
     in LHCb::L0DUReport
 
  from now both L0_DECISION and L0_DUMDECISION are *types* 
